1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,900
You know what a 401k plan is. Now, tonight I may have to explain it at some length, but this morning we're just going to go from there.

2
00:00:06,900 --> 00:00:14,200
The other thing I want to let you in on is that every Tuesday when you're preaching, Carol Gailey gives you a call.

3
